title: Hannah Dodd (actress)
summary: Hannah Francesca Katie Dodd (born 17 May 1995) is an English actress and model. She began her career in modeling and trained as a dancer before starring in the Hulu teen series Find Me in Paris (2018–2020). She has since appeared in the Netflix film Enola Holmes 2 (2022). She is set to play Francesca, the sixth Bridgerton child, in the period drama Bridgerton, also on Netflix.
